                    <ab>(..7..Bernar)do viris excelentissimo <rs key="#Emperor/king">rege</rs> …
                        Placuit adque convinit inter <persName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Missus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            ref="#people/119">Petrone</persName> vir venerabilis <rs key="#Abbots"
                            >abbas</rs> designato <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> qui
                        ..45..<placeName key="#Fruits/vegetables" ref="#places/">Sadriano</placeName> ud in Dei
                        nomine inter se commutare deverint sicut ad presente die commutaverunt
                        d..34..sa commutatione rebus de iura monasterii sui, qui est fundatum in <rs
                            key="#City_territory">finibus</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Monasteries #City_territory" ref="#places/262"
                            >Laude</placeName>, locus qui nominatur Sadriano ..20.. fundamenti in
                        suo proprio edificavet, et de ipso <persName><name ref="Manipertus"
                                >Maniperto</name></persName> devenit ipsii monasterio in potestate
                        monasterii <orgName
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Monasteries #Abbots"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47"><placeName ref="#places/15"
                                >Nonantole</placeName></orgName>, pri..25.. ex omnibus quasquas ad
                        iura monasterii advenerunt de quondam <persName><name ref="Seso"
                                >Sesone</name></persName> de <rs key="#Vici">vico</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Vici #Rivers #Petiae #Forests #Maiores" ref="#places/"
                            >Frexianuco</placeName> …, seo et iuge una de <rs key="#Forests"
                            >selva</rs> et campo insimul tenente qui dicitur de <persName><name
                                ref="Guntruda">Guntruda</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Teofridus">Teofre</name></persName> in ipso vico Frexianuco,
                        prope <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio</rs> Calendone; et alia iuge in ipso fundo
                        Frexianuco qui dicitur de <persName><name ref="Sigebertus"
                            >Sichiperto</name></persName> prope ispius <persName
                            key="#vassusOf #Commutatio"><name ref="Gumbertus"
                            >Gumperto</name></persName>; adque terra <rs key="#Maiores"
                            >haratorias</rs>
                        <rs key="#Petiae">petiolas</rs> quattuor in ipso fundo Frexianuco, … Simul
                        et dedet eidem Gumperti ipse abbas rebus ipsis de iura ipsius <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterii Sancti Petri</orgName> qui sunt positis in
                        finibus Laude, locus qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Chestnuts #Hay/fodder" ref="#places/"
                            >Mamilasco</placeName>, tam <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casalibus</rs> seo campis, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, silvis,
                            <rs key="#Chestnuts">castenetis</rs> … Ad vice recipet suprascripto
                        Petro abbas ad iam nominato Gumperto simulque in commutatione nomine ad
                        parte suprascripto monasterio rebus iuris suis, qui sunt positis in ipso
                        fundo Sadriano prope ipso monasterio Sancti Petri, qui eidem Gumperto ex <rs
                            key="#Commutatio">commutationem</rs> advenit de <persName
                            key="#Commutatio #Bishops">Petro</persName> vir <orgName
                            key="#Mother_churches #Bishops #Commutatio"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1400">beatus sancte Laudensis <rs
                                key="#Mother_churches">Ecclesie</rs></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>. Hoc est casalibus seo campis, pratis,
                        silvis, astalariis, ribis, ingressis, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">accessionibus usibusque
                            aquarum</rs>, tantum reversato mihi Gumperto de ipsa sorte qui mihi in
                        concambio de ipso episcopus advenet, iuge una de terra haratoria prope de
                        curte mea de Frexianuco. Et dedet ipse Gumperto ad parte ipsius monasterii
                        de sorte illa qui eidem Gumperto ex comparatione de <persName key="#Salian"
                                ><name ref="Ansbaldus">Hinsenpaldo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Salian">franco</rs> advenet, hoc est petias de terra duas cum <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">arboris</rs> super se abente quot sunt in fundo
                        Sadriano de ista parte via qui perge de Cassiola de <rs key="#Villas"
                            >villa</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Villas" ref="#places/">Crisia</placeName>, … Et adcesserunt super ipsis
                        rebus previdendo et extimando <rs key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >missi</rs> ipsius abbatis, idest <persName
                            key="#Priests #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Monks"><name
                                ref="Letus">Aloeto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> ipsius
                        monasterii Nonantole seo et <persName key="#Prevosts"><name
                                key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Prevosts" ref="Garipertus"
                                >Gariperto</name></persName> presbiter er <rs key="#Prevosts"
                            >perpositus</rs> ipsius monasterii Sancti Petri una cum idoneis omenis
                        corum nominas suptus adnexa sunt. … Hacto ad suprascripto vico Frexianuco. +
                        Ego Gumperto <rs key="#vassusOf">vasso domini regi</rs> in hanc cartula
                        commutationis a me facta manu mea propria subscripsi. Signum + manus
                            <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"><name ref="Gausbertus"
                                >Gausperti</name></persName> de vico <placeName
                                    key="#Vici #Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness" ref="#places/">Arsiate</placeName> qui
                        ipsis rebus extimavet teste extetet. Signum + manus <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"><name ref="Deusdedit"
                                >Deodati</name></persName> de vico <placeName
                                    key="#Vici #Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness" ref="#places/">Agello</placeName> qui
                        ipsis rebus <rs key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">extimavet</rs>
                        <rs key="#Witness">teste</rs> extetet. Signum + manus <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"><name ref="Gispertus"
                                >Giseperti</name></persName> de vico <placeName
                                    key="#Vici #Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness" ref="#places/">Casolate</placeName> qui
                        ipsis rebus extimavet teste extetet. Signum + manus <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"><name ref="Ambrosius"
                                >Ambrosiuni</name></persName> de Casolate qui ipsis rebus extimavet
                        teste extetet. Signum + manus <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"><name ref="Angelfredus"
                                >Angelfridi</name></persName> filio <persName><name ref="Donnulus"
                                >Donnoloni</name></persName> de <placeName
                                    key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness" ref="#places/">Fabriano</placeName> qui ipsis
                        rebus extimavet teste extetet. + Ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Magnus">Magnus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> posttradita conplivi et dedit. + <rs
                            key="#Copy">Exenplaria</rs> per manum <persName key="#Notary #Copy"
                                ><name ref="Martianus">Marciani</name></persName> notario.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
